text: Hannah and Her Sisters is a 1986 American comedy drama movie directed by Woody Allen (who also stars) and starring Michael Caine, Mia Farrow, Carrie Fisher, Barbara Hershey, Lloyd Nolan, Maureen O'Sullivan, Daniel Stern, Max von Sydow, Dianne Wiest. It was distributed by Orion Pictures and was nominated for 7 Oscars and won 3 Academy Awards in 1987. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1986 comedy-drama movies Category:American comedy-drama movies Category:Movies directed by Woody Allen Category:American independent movies
title: Hannah and Her Sisters
